SYNOPSIS
    int P_PAGEWIDTH  "PageWidth"

    int Set(P_PAGEWIDTH, int value)
    int Query(P_PAGEWIDTH)
      or
    int SetPageWidth(int value)
    int QueryPageWidth()

DESCRIPTION
    The pagewidth for the interactive user.

EXAMPLE
    Query(P_PAGEWIDTH);

AVAILABILITY
    Include: <properties.h>

    Availability: /std/player(/misc)

SEE ALSO
    player(S)
